[
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413360",
        "quote": "I want to take TSA to the next level.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Pistole",
            "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413360"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Next",
                "url": "/topics/next"
            },
            {
                "name": "Take",
                "url": "/topics/take"
            },
            {
                "name": "TSA",
                "url": "/topics/tsa"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413363",
        "quote": "The bottom line is how do we best provide for the security of the traveling public in light of a determined enemy who is adept at constructing well-designed, well-concealed devices which would not show up in a walk-through metal detector? We're trying to employ the best technology to identify any possible threat.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Pistole",
            "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413363"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Line",
                "url": "/topics/line"
            },
            {
                "name": "Show",
                "url": "/topics/show"
            },
            {
                "name": "Employ",
                "url": "/topics/employ"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413341",
        "quote": "We want to be sensitive to people's concerns about privacy about their personal being and things, while ensuring that everybody on every flight has been properly screened.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Pistole",
            "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413341"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Flight",
                "url": "/topics/flight"
            },
            {
                "name": "Everybody",
                "url": "/topics/everybody"
            },
            {
                "name": "Been",
                "url": "/topics/been"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413342",
        "quote": "I particularly recognize that reasonable people can disagree as to what that proper balance or blend is between privacy and security and safety.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Pistole",
            "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413342"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Reasonable",
                "url": "/topics/reasonable"
            },
            {
                "name": "Particularly",
                "url": "/topics/particularly"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413343",
        "quote": "But what I want to assure and reassure the public is we are concerned about your safety, your security, and your privacy. Let's work together in partnership to ensure that we can have the best way forward.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Pistole",
            "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413343"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Partnership",
                "url": "/topics/partnership"
            },
            {
                "name": "Best Way",
                "url": "/topics/best_way"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413344",
        "quote": "Our pat-down approach is very similar to what is being utilized in Europe and, as we know, around the world. It's even much more thorough in other parts of the world.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Pistole",
            "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413344"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Very",
                "url": "/topics/very"
            },
            {
                "name": "Similar",
                "url": "/topics/similar"
            },
            {
                "name": "Other",
                "url": "/topics/other"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413345",
        "quote": "And so we try to address those concerns in every way possible, recognizing, again, in the final analysis, everybody on that flight wants to be assured with the highest level of confidence that everybody else on that flight has been properly screened, and including me and you and everybody.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Pistole",
            "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413345"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Flight",
                "url": "/topics/flight"
            },
            {
                "name": "Been",
                "url": "/topics/been"
            },
            {
                "name": "Highest Level",
                "url": "/topics/highest_level"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413346",
        "quote": "I want to improve TSA's counterterrorism focus through intelligence and cutting edge technology, support the TSA workforce, and strengthen the agency's relationships with stakeholders and the traveling public. All of these priorities are interconnected and are vital to TSA's mission - and I would say, all of our collective mission.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Pistole",
            "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413346"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Through",
                "url": "/topics/through"
            },
            {
                "name": "Interconnected",
                "url": "/topics/interconnected"
            },
            {
                "name": "TSA",
                "url": "/topics/tsa"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413347",
        "quote": "The reason we are doing these types of pat downs and using the advanced imagery technology is trying to take the latest intelligence and how we know al Qaeda and affiliates want to hurt us, they want to bring down whether it is passenger air craft or cargo aircraft.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Pistole",
            "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413347"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Doing",
                "url": "/topics/doing"
            },
            {
                "name": "Reason",
                "url": "/topics/reason"
            },
            {
                "name": "Advanced",
                "url": "/topics/advanced"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413348",
        "quote": "The bottom line is, if somebody doesn't go through proper security screening, they're not going to go on the flight.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Pistole",
            "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413348"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Through",
                "url": "/topics/through"
            },
            {
                "name": "Flight",
                "url": "/topics/flight"
            },
            {
                "name": "Screening",
                "url": "/topics/screening"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413361",
        "quote": "We save limited resources in terms of who we are physically screening. The approach will allow us to pay more attention to those potential terrorists.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Pistole",
            "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413361"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Allow",
                "url": "/topics/allow"
            },
            {
                "name": "Screening",
                "url": "/topics/screening"
            },
            {
                "name": "Limited",
                "url": "/topics/limited"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413362",
        "quote": "Pilots are not the threat.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Pistole",
            "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413362"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Pilots",
                "url": "/topics/pilots"
            },
            {
                "name": "Threat",
                "url": "/topics/threat"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413364",
        "quote": "We put people of concern on the watch list or the no-fly list, so we have a number of layers of security beyond the airport checkpoint. We gather as much information about a passenger as the law allows without profiling.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Pistole",
            "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413364"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Law",
                "url": "/topics/law"
            },
            {
                "name": "About",
                "url": "/topics/about"
            },
            {
                "name": "Checkpoint",
                "url": "/topics/checkpoint"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413422",
        "quote": "I did not want to provide a blueprint or roadmap for the terrorists, saying 'Here are our new security procedures'.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Pistole",
            "url": "/quotes/john_pistole_413422"
        },
